**Additional Notes:**
- The tire well appears to be intact without any visible damage.
- No other visible damage was noted on the front fender or surrounding areas.

**Conclusion:**
The front fender (right side) of the vehicle exhibits noticeable damage, primarily consisting of dents, scratches, and paint chipping. Further inspection may be required to assess the extent of the damage and determine the appropriate course of action for repair.
